      "created_at": "2021-01-02T15:13:24.478Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi. I\u2019ve just signed up and I have a Bkool Smart Pro 2. I\u2019ve tried using one of the plans TD makes available, plus a workout I\u2019ve used with other softwae and which I know works, but in the TD app, the ERG/Free-ride button is not available to click. It is there but is in effect, greyed out.</p>\n<p>The turbo talks to the app as it records the power I produce, but it doesn\u2019t change resistance. Interestingly the RPM feed isn\u2019t working either.</p>\n<p>I\u2019ve used it on a couple of Android tablets with the same result.</p>\n<p>Can anyone help please ?</p>\n<p>Thanks</p>",
