      "created_at": "2021-01-03T16:27:46.344Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes but this CABLE device converts Ant+ to FTMS which is the current bluetooth standard for fitness machines.  The Bkool has a non-standardd type of bluetooth.  There are really 3-primary bluetooth types now.  Neo + Wahoo + FTMS.  Tacx uses FTMS for all their devices other than Neo for example and Wahoo is switching to FTMS.</p>",
